feeds.title: resident evil 7
feeds.description: Resident evil 7. The horror survival series turned to first person view aimed to provide an extreme chilling experiences. And boy! did they more than accomplish this objective. RE7 is one of the scariest among its series and the storyline is refreshing too! p.s to gain the most experience out of this game, off the light, close the door and plugged in. *warning* Not for the faint-hearted

comments.commentInfo: indeed, I peed my pants 5mins into the game. LOL

feeds.title: 30 years of wait is over!
feeds.description: In the darkest year of 2020! there is finally a bright spot in the town of Liverpool. Long have the kopites waited for their glory to return and what a manner it was returned. 30 years of wait, 5 times of close to winning. they won by 20 over points and with such relentless pursue in winning! what a team! what a manager! In these dark years, the only constant was Anfield who never cease to roar. Now they pride on their team and this man ==> Jurgen Klopp. This is ANFIELD! p.s. to man-utd fans, more to come!
